    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi there @HamzaInPerth, thanks for reaching out.\r\n`algoliasearch/lite` is part of the `algoliasearch` npm package. I think you're right, InstantSearch types are using the client's types, so either it should reimplement them to be fully independent, or list the client as a peer dependency.\r\n@Haroenv do you agree with this?\r\n\r\nQuestion to @HamzaInPerth : are you not reusing the client types for your custom client?",
