    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes, this is expected, the types otherwise would have to be fully retyped here, which would be a source of confusion and possible errors. We might need to think of a special solution, as it's not really a dependency, but maybe it can be considered one. algoliasearch is required to be installed when using typescript, but doesn't need to be used. \r\n\r\nSynthetic default imports are needed indeed.",
